Beyond the Horror: Asylum, is an unofficial American Horror Story Live Review Show. Hosted by MaryGirl Moody, Maisie Andrews, Casey Soper, and Tami Sifford. We discuss and review each episode of American Horror Story Asylum. Join the Freaks of AHS on Facebook and Beyond the Horror.
